Products.RichDescription:
Ladyfingers or "Savoiardi" take their name from the original region of Savoy which included the region of Sardinia in Italy.
Savoiardi originated in the late 15th century at the court of the Duchy of Savoy where they were created to mark the occasion of a visit by the King of France.
Today whilst ladyfingers are seen in many shapes and forms, Ital chooses to produce Savoiardi using the traditional recipe used by the master patisserie chefs of years gone by.

Products.RichDescription:
A blend of finely chopped chilli, garlic & ginger. Simply coat your favourite protein before cooking for an instant flavour boost that will make any meal delicious.

A blend of finely chopped chilli, garlic & ginger. Simply coat your favourite protein before cooking for an instant flavour boost that will make any meal delicious.

Perfect with chicken, beef or tofu. For something different, try on your favourite plant-based meat alternative or vegetables.

To create a delicious dinner in just 20 mins, simply...
1. Coat 500 g of chicken, beef or tofu in the Chilli, Garlic & Ginger seasoning.
2. Fry in a non-stick pan, bake or BBQ until cooked through.
3. Serve with your favourite vegetables or side salad.

No Artificial Colours, Flavours or Preservatives.

Blended with MasterFoods Herbs & Spices.
